  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT346-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">tōḻi kiḻattiyai iravukkuṟi nayappak kūṟiyatu. </p>


        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Spoken [to inform HIM] that SHE would grant night
          trysts, by the confidante. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT346">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> nākupiṭi nayanta muḷaikkōṭ ṭiḷaṅkaḷiṟu</l>
          <l> kuṉṟa naṇṇik kuṟava rārppa</l>
          <l> maṉṟam pōḻu nāṭaṉ ṟōḻi</l>
          <l> cuṉaippūṅ kuvaḷait toṭalai tantun</l>
          <l> tiṉaippuṉa maruṅkiṟ paṭukiḷi yōppiyuṅ</l>
          <l> kālai vantu mālaip poḻuti</l>
          <l> ṉallaka nayantutā ṉuyaṅkic</l>
          <l> collavu mākā taḵki yōṉē.</l>


        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>The man from a land, friend,</l>
          <l rend="indent">where a young elephant bull with sprouting tusks,</l>
          <l rend="indent">who longed for the young female, [usually] staying in the hills </l>
          <l rend="indent">crosses the village common, so that the hill people shout,</l>
          <l>giving a waterlily chaplet of flowers from the mountain pool</l>
          <l>and scaring away the parakeets falling into the millet field</l>
          <l>having come in the morning, at evening time</l>
          <l>he longed in [his] good mind, became weak himself</l>
          <l>[and] even without speaking he [was] dejected.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
